OL,3,CUK increasingly exposed to health-
OL,4,Cthreatening extreme heat
OL,6,FPeople in the UK are increasingly
OL,7,Fexposed to dangerous extreme heat, as
OL,8,Fglobal health threats of climate
OL,9,Fchange reach record-breaking levels,
OL,10,Fexperts warn.
OL,12,FA report by the Lancet Countdown on
OL,13,FHealth and Climate Change found there
OL,14,Fis a heightened risk of heat-related
OL,15,Fillness and mortality in the UK, with
OL,16,Fan extra nine deaths per 100,000
OL,17,Fpeople on average in 2013-2022.
